 class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="50:10" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-50-10">وَالنَّخْلَ بَاسِقَاتٍ لَّهَا طَلْعٌ نَّضِيدٌ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/50/10" target="_blank" title="سورة ق"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.4caD5"/><p id="102.B9Ec7"/><p id="102.a5699"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="50:11"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="50:11" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-50-11">رِّزْقًا لِّلْعِبَادِ ۖ وَأَحْيَيْنَا بِهِ بَلْدَةً مَّيْتًا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ الْخُرُوجُ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/50/11" target="_blank" title="سورة ق"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.2eB6e"/><p id="102.732f6"/><p id="102.Aa10e"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="50:12"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="50:12" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-50-12">كَذَّبَتْ قَبْلَهُمْ قَوْمُ نُوحٍ وَأَصْحَابُ الرَّسِّ وَثَمُودُ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/50/12" target="_blank" title="سورة ق"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.B4B5D"/><p id="102.95b3b"/><p id="102.88c32"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="50:13"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="50:13" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-50-13">وَعَادٌ وَفِرْعَوْنُ وَإِخْوَانُ لُوطٍ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/50/13" target="_blank" title="سورة ق"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.bcE2e"/><p id="102.8B0FF"/><p id="102.D3Fa4"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="50:14"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="50:14" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-50-14">وَأَصْحَابُ الْأَيْكَةِ وَقَوْمُ تُبَّعٍ ۚ كُلٌّ كَذَّبَ الرُّسُلَ فَحَقَّ وَعِيدِ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/50/14" target="_blank" title="سورة ق"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.d22cc"/><p id="102.F2de0"/><p id="102.DCbe3"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsi